Module atu.software
Package ie.atu.sw.services

Interface ExaminationPaperService

All Known Implementing Classes:
ExaminationPaperServiceImpl
public interface ExaminationPaperService
Interface for services handling examination papers. Defines the operations for adding, retrieving, updating, and listing examination papers.

  • Method Details

    • addExaminationPaper

      void addExaminationPaper()
      Adds a new examination paper. The implementation should handle the input and creation of a new ExaminationPaper object.

    • getExaminationPaper

      ExaminationPaper getExaminationPaper(String moduleCode)
      Retrieves an examination paper based on the given module code.
      Parameters:
      moduleCode - The module code associated with the examination paper.
      Returns:
      The ExaminationPaper object associated with the given module code, or null if not found.

    • updateExaminationPaper

      void updateExaminationPaper(String moduleCode, ExaminationPaper paper)
      Updates the information of an existing examination paper.
      Parameters:
      moduleCode - The module code of the examination paper to be updated.
      paper - The new ExaminationPaper object with updated information.

    • getAllExaminationPapers

      List<ExaminationPaper> getAllExaminationPapers()
      Retrieves a list of all examination papers.
      Returns:
      A list of all ExaminationPaper objects.

    • listAllExaminationPapers

      void listAllExaminationPapers()
      Lists all the examination papers. This method should display the details of all examination papers.
